\n$\\frac{1}{2}(n-1)$ $=$ $\\frac{1}{2}$), and the three manifolds case ($n$ $=$\n$2$, $\\rho$ $=$ $1$). Finally, for $j$ $=$ $n-1$, $n$ $\\geq$ $4$, our result\nimproves the best known bound in the manifolds with cusps case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Nov 2020 18:07:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-17"}
