s of meVSL on various cosmological observations\nincluding BBN, CMB, SZE, BAO, SNe, GWs, H, SL, and $\\Delta \\alpha$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Nov 2020 11:42:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Aug 2021 23:33:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-27"}
